news.title: Pune: Properties with solar water heating systems double in five years
news.para: While the number of properties with solar water heating systems stood at 29,000 in the year 2017-18, it surged to 58,000 in 2021-22, the report stated.

news.title: Hubballi-Dharwad civic body ranks second in digitisation of property records in Karnataka
news.para: The HDMC, which regulates the infrastructural assets and civic facilities in the twin cities of Hubballi and Dharwad including properties, transactions and their administration, had launched an online management system that keeps a record of property ownership, transactions and status.

news.title: DTP demolishes encroachments, illegal colony in Panchkula
news.para: District planning officer (DTP) Gunjan Verma said that the drive was conducted under the Controlled Urban Area Act and Urban Area Act of the Town and Country Planning department.
